Prometheus Tornado Instrumentator

This project is a Tornado-focused Prometheus instrumentator inspired by
trallnag/prometheus-fastapi-instrumentator, which is licensed under the ISC
License.

The initial semantic-parity baseline was audited against:

- Repository: https://github.com/trallnag/prometheus-fastapi-instrumentator
